, retinitis, and atypical pneumonia can also occur. Cat-scratch disease can atypically present as parinaud oculoglandular syndrome (unilateral conjunctivitis and preauricular lymphadenopathy).", "synonyms": "Bartonellosis due to Bartonella henselae infection, ", "prevalence": "1-9 / 100 000", "inheritance": "Not applicable\u00a0", "age_of_onset": "All ages", "icd_10": "A28.1", "umls": "C0007361\u00a0 C0238909", "mesh": "D002372", "gard": "27", "meddra": "10007729"}, {"name": "Bart-Pumphrey-Syndrom", "sub_name": "Knuckle-Pads-Leukonychie-sensorineurale Schwerh\u00f6rigkeit-palmoplantare Hyperkeratose-Syndrom", "german_description": "Eine Kurzbeschreibung der Krankheit wird derzeit erstellt. Weiterf\u00fchrende Informationen zu dieser Krankheit k\u00f6nnen \u00fcber das Menu  am unteren Bildrand abgerufen werden.", "english": 1, "defenition": "A rare, syndromic genetic deafness disease characterized by symmetric or asymmetirc knuckle pads (typically located on the distal and interphalangeal joints), leukonychia, diffuse palmoplantar keratoderma, and congenital, mild to moderate sensorineural deafness.", "synonyms": "Bart-Pumphrey syndrome, Knuckle pads-leukonychia-sensorineural deafness-palmoplantar keratoderma syndrome, Knuckle pads-leukonychia-sensorineural hearing loss-palmoplantar hyperkeratosis syndrome, Knuckle pads-leukonychia-sensorineural hearing loss-palmoplantar keratoderma syndrome, ", "prevalence": "<1 / 1 000 000", "age_of_onset": "Childhood", "icd_10": "Q82.8", "omim": "149200", "umls": "C0266004", "gard": "3125"}, {"name": "Bartsocas-Papas-Syndrom", "german_description": "Eine Kurzbeschreibung der Krankheit wird derzeit erstellt. Weiterf\u00fchrende Informationen zu dieser Krankheit k\u00f6nnen \u00fcber das Menu  am unteren Bildrand abgerufen werden.", "english": 1, "defenition": "Bartsocas-Papas syndrome is a rare, inherited, popliteal pterygium syndrome (see this term) characterized by severe popliteal webbing, microcephaly, a typical face with shor